<p>An element used to create a status bar, usually placed along the bottom of a window. It is virtually equivalent to a standard box, but may be rendered differently. Contains <span class="script">XULElem("statusbarpanel")</span>s&lt;.</p>
<dl> <dt>Properties</dt> <dd><span class="script">template.PrefAnch("p-", "accessibleType")</span></dd>
</dl>
<h3 name="Examples">Examples</h3>
<pre>
&lt;statusbar&gt;
  &lt;statusbarpanel label="Left panel"/&gt;
  &lt;spacer flex="1"/&gt;
  &lt;progressmeter mode="determined" value="82"/&gt;
  &lt;statusbarpanel label="Right panel"/&gt;
&lt;/statusbar&gt;
</pre>
